long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension simplifies the process of saving the profile addresses of interesting people on professional/social networking sites and retrieving your session cookie for each time you use expertise.tv a.i.R3.

expertise.tv a.i.R3 enables you to 

Build a list of ideal client targets as you browse professional and social networking sites.
Develop engaging content that attracts your target list to you.
Engage with your target list and have conversations with them.

How does this extension work?

Once logged in to your expertise.tv a.i.R3 dashboard, this extension will allow you to save the profile urls of people on social and professional networking sites like an online address book. It will also enable you to seamlessly retrieve the session ID of any site that you are connected to, when using expertise.tv a.i.R3.

Please contact our live chat support if you have any questions: https://expertise.tv/contact
